dbone Arrow<br/>11-99 ARC + Longbow = 5 Bloodbone Arrow<br/>11-99 ARC + Longbow = 5 Poisonbone Arrow<br/>11-99 ARC + Longbow = 4 Serpant Arrow<br/><br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 3 Sleepbone Arrow<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 2 Sleepbone Arrow<br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 6 Rotbone Arrow<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 6 Rotbone Arrow<br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 6 Coldbone Arrow<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 6 Coldbone Arrow<br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 5 Bloodbone Arrow<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 3 Bloodbone Arrow<br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 3 Poisonbone Arrow<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 2 Poisonbone Arrow<br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 3 Serpant Arrow<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 1 Serpant Arrow<br/><br/>Bonus: <br/>11 ARC + Serpent Bow   = 23 ANY Arrows to Poison<br/>99 ARC + Serpent Bow = 8 ANY Arrows to Poison</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16616906" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16616906" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">8</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>99</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>1</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16616906"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16616906" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16616906"></ul>